[SPEAKER_06]: I'm very happy to have you here.

911
01:23:14,181 --> 01:23:22,445
[SPEAKER_06]: And please, if any questions, concerns, comments, ideas come up, feel free to shoot me an email so that we can add them to the agenda.

912
01:23:22,485 --> 01:23:24,266
[SPEAKER_06]: I believe our next meeting is January 24th.

913
01:23:25,924 --> 01:23:28,286
[SPEAKER_06]: So, I hope to to see you all there.

914
01:23:28,306 --> 01:23:32,389
[SPEAKER_06]: You're welcome to join if you'd like, don't feel like you have to remember.

915
01:23:32,429 --> 01:23:40,514
[SPEAKER_08]: I know I'll talk to the planning commission about to see the planning department to see if it would be wise to have a representative.

916
01:23:47,899 --> 01:23:48,419
[SPEAKER_01]: Sounds good.

917
01:23:49,520 --> 01:23:50,521
[SPEAKER_05]: Thank you so much for you.

918
01:23:53,096 --> 01:23:53,760
[SPEAKER_05]: Happy New Year.

919
01:23:54,082 --> 01:23:55,291
[SPEAKER_05]: Happy New Year.

920
01:23:55,311 --> 01:23:56,740
[SPEAKER_05]: Thank you, Gabriella.

921
01:23:56,921 --> 01:23:57,425
[SPEAKER_05]: Good job.

922
